NIPER

●As per the INFORMATION BOUCHER published on the NIPER- Hyderabad official website total seats on NIPER is around 968.

●But, Below every seat matrix they mentioned that the seat may vary at the time of admission.

Estimation: Any student having an AIR (All India Rank ) below 968 in GENERAL CATEGORY have maximum chances to get a seat in any of the mentioned NIPER
